				   april repl

apl repl using the april library for common lisp.

inputs are evaluated using the 'april-f' macro from the april library.

installation:

  install roswell (https://roswell.github.io)

  run the command:

    ros install goranpjevic/april-repl

system commands:

  )load  - load an apl file

  )exit  - exit repl

example usage:

  > 1+1
  2
  > 5⊃1+⍳100
  6
  > (+/÷≢)⍳5
  3
  > a←10
  
  > a+1
  11
  > )load
  load apl file: test.apl
  > b
  20
  > )exit

more information at:

  https://github.com/phantomics/april
